{"tid":53473,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［膊頭有花既全部同我入黎］連登駁嘴工藝訓練中心","createTime":"2016-12-24T17:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T01:35:03.000Z","uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9ec90e84417fe334256220eea87380c0da20fc","tid":53473,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"各位聖誕快樂，<br />\n呢個鐘數入得黎既都係有哂軍階既毒撚，心靈脆弱又成日比人串親<br />\n重要係比人串完第二日先諗到點駁嘴「屌，早知咁講啦！」<br />\n為左唔好重覆昨日既錯誤，特此開設此中心<br />\n快啲留低擊傷你的石頭，等各位連登既30cm 做你智囊團，見招拆招<br />\n他日見到舊敵，何止可以串到佢口疾疾，嚇到佢fatality都得<br />\n<br />\n我先：<br />\n我的朋友不是我（男），比個senior（男）話：「我覺得你唔夠elegant。」<br />\n<br />\n利申：毒撚等被救"},{"pid":"38a719342077ce51f28f5bfc4ca806c78525f206","tid":53473,"uid":59089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"senior（男）話：「我覺得你唔夠elegant。」<br />\n你應：「我夠gentleman 咪得囉」"},{"pid":"f0c14cfa78652f7fb698eab5be1539a72c76baeb","tid":53473,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>senior（男）話：「我覺得你唔夠elegant。」<br />\n你應：「我夠gentleman 咪得囉」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢做飾品店sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢問我點反擊我都唔識應佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85354bc7797fb8031d6be32c5d1a333b393431e7","tid":53473,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"洗咩駁呀<br />\n一個冷笑先係高招<br />\n夠對方估足三日三夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da33cf9ef0377e686b8998554e033ad1f0f4550f","tid":53473,"uid":53378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}